# coverage.map — the feature inventory (the mandate).
# Copy to your project root as ./coverage.map and edit.
# One feature per line:  module | Feature name | optional-route-glob
# Lines starting with # are ignored. A feature is "covered" when at least one
# testcase has a matching `module:` (or a final URL matching the route glob).

home     | Home / landing page
login    | Login flow              | **/login
signup   | Account registration   | **/signup
search   | Search results          | **/results**
checkout | Checkout & payment      | **/checkout/**
profile  | User profile settings   | **/account/**
